metadata.name: RHIDER #1
metadata.description: RHIDER is a digital art collection with 5,155 PFP which are stored on the Ethereum blockchain and are based on little rhinoceros. The rarities are X/A/B/C/D. Under every armor there is one little rhinoceros with an innocent inner heart. We arm ourselves, and we will make some noises and changes in this world. RHIDER believes that every individual has their own shining spot, we hope that we can expand our territory with all of our enhanced individuals, the future and unlimited possibilities of RHIDER come from the magnificent assertiveness and braveness of every enhanced individual, and all of them are RHIDERs. We aim for gathering all capable people around the world and build the strongest community ever, together we will achieve something big in web3.
